{"word":"Καππαδοκίζω","slug":"Καππαδοκίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>Καππαδοκίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:Καππαδόκαι'><el>Καππαδόκαι</el></a>\n<p/><i>to favour the Cappadocians</i>,<b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to play the Cappadocian</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/>"}]}